Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.10,0:01:37.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fafner Mark Elf, lançar!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.03,0:01:59.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aterrissagem do Fafner Mark Elf foi completada.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.83,0:02:01.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Desabilitando o piloto automático.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.68,0:02:05.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Mark Elf estará operando agora através da Nibelung do piloto...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.48,0:02:07.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.00,0:02:12.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\shad0\bord0.5\fnBook Antiqua\fs48\i1\an3}Gelo
